#: ../../S/scratch.rst:5
msgid "scratch"
msgstr "scratch"

#: ../../S/scratch.rst:8
msgid ""
"[from scratchpad] adj. Describes a data structure or recording medium "
"attached to a machine for testing or temporary-use purposes; one that can be"
" :ref:`scribble`\\d on without loss. Usually in the combining forms scratch "
"memory, scratch register, scratch disk, scratch tape, scratch volume. See "
"also :ref:`scratch-monkey`\\."
msgstr ""
"[scratchpad(メモ帳)から] 形容詞 テストや一時利用の目的でマシンに接続された、データ構造または記録媒体を表す。失われても構わずに\\ "
":ref:`scribble`\\ できるもの。たいてい複合形で、scratch memory、scratch register、scratch "
"disk、scratch tape、scratch volumeのように使われる。\\ :ref:`scratch-monkey`\\ も参照。"

#: ../../S/scratch.rst:14
msgid "[primarily IBM, also Commodore] vt. To delete (as in a file)."
msgstr "[主にIBM、Commodoreでも] 他動詞 (ファイルなどを)削除すること。"
